==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unfaith
<hw>Un*faith"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Absence or want of
faith; faithlessness; distrust; unbelief.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Faith and <qex>unfaith</qex> can ne'er be equal powers:⟦br⟧
<qex>Unfaith</qex> in aught is want of faith in all.</q>
<rj><qau>Tennyson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unfaithful</ent>⟦br⟧
